uba uzi uko mama wawe yishwe ?
yee , nk' uko nbibabwiye icyo hari mu gitondo , hari ku itariki makumyabiri na zirindwi z' ukwa kane [ 27 /04 /1994 ] . uraumva jenoside yari imaze ibyumweru bibiri itangiye . hari mu gitondo nbabwiye ko yari arwaye ... yari arwaye malariya afite intege nkeya , baraza baramufata . babanje kubicaza hasi , bamaze nk' amasaha agera kuri abiri baicaye . ubwo hari igitero cy' abantu ariko ngo harimo abantu bagerageza kubasabair imbabazi , bakibainginga ngo ntibabicae . ubwo bari nk' abantu bagera kuri mirongo itandatu [ 60 ] . barabafata nawe baramufata yarakenyeye ibitenge kubera ko yari arwaye ataitira akenyeye ibitenge hose kugirango imbeho ntimufatae , kuko nta makote yari afite yari yifubitse kugirango imbeho ntimufatae , kandi hari ku zuba . baramufata baramuzamura bamuryamaish ahantu , bamuryamaish hasi baramubwira ngo niubikae inda , nrangiza arebae hasi barangije bamurashe isasu rimwe mu mutawe arapfa .
