numva ubuzima bw' ejo hazaza buzaba bwiza . kurenza ubwashize uko buri bumeze mu myaka cumi ishize .
ubona u rwanda nk' igihugu rukwaiye kukura somo ki ku bibaye ?
jyae nbona isomo u rwanda ruvanamo ... ... nbona bibaye mu rwanda kuko u rwanda n' igihugu gitoya kandi cyiza , nbona abanyarwanda riba isomo y' uko bagomba kukundana , gufashanya nicyo kintu kituma u rwanda ... kandi no kutaibagirwa ... kutaibagirwa ibyahise .
kuhora baibuka kandi bakatekereza gufashanya .
